WEBVTT

00:00:27.160 --> 00:00:31.336
is the hallmark
of every American workplace.

00:00:31.360 --> 00:00:34.816
There are thousands of images like these.

00:00:34.840 --> 00:00:38.256
Just put the term "working mother"
into any Google image search engine,

00:00:38.280 --> 00:00:39.536
stock photo site.

00:00:39.560 --> 00:00:41.016
They're all over the Internet,

00:00:41.040 --> 00:00:43.416
they're topping
blog posts and news pieces,

00:00:43.440 --> 00:00:47.776
and I've become kind of obsessed with them
and the lie that they tell us

00:00:47.800 --> 00:00:49.776
and the comfort that they give us,

00:00:49.800 --> 00:00:53.216
that when it comes
to new working motherhood in America,

00:00:53.240 --> 00:00:55.016
everything's fine.

00:00:55.040 --> 00:00:56.616
But it's not fine.

00:00:56.640 --> 00:01:00.056
As a country, we are sending
millions of women back to work